{"tid":1607222,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［DSE請入］考完試對網上答案不要太認真","createTime":"2019-09-30T18:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T13:42:56.000Z","uid":302834,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88bc92721dc50ac71ac1db9fdff1e12623a05f84","tid":1607222,"uid":302834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T18:30:00.000Z","msg":"唔係想插人，我都知係人都有錯既<br />\n我只係想同各位講 好多人一考完DSE就上網搵「名師」對答案，但想提提CHing們，唔好信100%，睇吓就好，唔好太認真<br />\n<br />\n例如呢位<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2auMKm7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2auMKm7.png&h=54b55dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一考完試就Po答案，但其實就算係名師 都未必啱曬<br />\n（申利：真係唔係串佢，佢好多答案都啱，串親佢既講句sor先）<br />\n<br />\nEng 2019 P1 佢既reference ans<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTcKv3N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTcKv3N.png&h=90486f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16iv 根本唔係space <br />\n係 control <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OiXOdho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOiXOdho.png&h=ffd3db0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePzwVvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePzwVvW.png&h=58e3f299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58NB6CH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58NB6CH.png&h=75d07878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n65ii都錯！<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有 第62題ii 佢份reference話唔比寫 extolling <br />\n但其實都照比分 （有圖有真相）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tx76Kqp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftx76Kqp.png&h=b6abcbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvimyiU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvimyiU.png&h=0810ca68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該仲有既.....唔搵啦，唔好搞到太難睇<br />\n所以，大家其實最好就唔好對答案，考曬先對啦！就算對咗，都唔好信曬，留一線希望啦！ 2020加油呀！<br />\n<br />\n利申：19DSE, 我考完有睇😂😂"},{"pi